flowchart TB
  subgraph RequestBoundary[Interactive request boundary]
    direction LR
    Browser[Untrusted browser input] --> WAF[Edge validation and rate limit]
    WAF --> Auth[Identity and server-derived tenant context]
    Auth --> Policy[Policy decision point]
    Policy --> API[Application boundary]
    API --> TenantStore[(Tenant fenced stores)]
  end
  subgraph ContentBoundary[Untrusted connector and model-content boundary]
    direction LR
    GitHub[Hostile GitHub payload] --> Connector[Isolated connector parser]
    Jira[Hostile Jira payload] --> Connector
    Connector --> Observation[Immutable normalized observation]
    Observation --> Model[Model context as data only]
    Model --> Schema[Structured output validation]
  end
  subgraph ActionBoundary[Sensitive action boundary]
    direction LR
    Schema --> ToolGateway[Tool policy gateway]
    ToolGateway --> Approval[Exact-payload dual approval]
    Approval --> JiraWrite[Allowlisted Jira write]
    JiraWrite --> Audit[(Tamper-evident audit)]
    ToolGateway --> Audit
  end
